OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FTroubles' deaths leave a wound that
OL,7,Fdoes "not simply heal with time", a
OL,8,Fgathering of bereaved families has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FAn event to mark European Day for
OL,12,FVictims of Terrorism was hosted by TUV
OL,13,FMLA Timothy Gaston at Stormont, and
OL,14,Fheard from family members of those
OL,15,Fkilled by groups including the IRA and
OL,16,FUVF, and a survivor of the 2017
OL,17,FWestminster Bridge Islamist-related
OL,18,Fterrorist attack.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
