OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FPastor Stephen Thompson lost his aunt,
OL,7,FYvonne Dunlop, who was killed by an
OL,8,FIRA firebomb in Ballymena in 1976.
OL,10,FMr Thompson's grandparents stepped in
OL,11,Fto raise her children, and he said the
OL,12,F"weight of losing a daughter in such a
OL,13,Fbrutal way was something no parent
OL,14,Fshould ever have to endure".
OL,16,F"My granddad was never the same after
OL,17,FYvonne's death, many of us believe he
OL,18,Fdied of a broken heart," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@[O]xD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"My daughter is exactly the same age
OL,7,FYvonne was back then. I can't even
OL,8,Fbegin to imagine the hurting that he
OL,9,Fsuffered.
OL,11,F"The grief never truly left him. The
OL,12,Fpain of burying his own child marked
OL,13,Fhim deeply and permanently."
OL,15,FHe spoke of the extended impact on his
OL,16,Ffamily, including them moving to
OL,17,FNottingham and his sister becoming
OL,18,Faddicted to drugs, and said violence
OL,19,F"does not stop at one act".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@\O]{D@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"When people speak about the Troubles,
OL,7,Fthe phrase can sound distant and
OL,8,Falmost clinical, but for families like
OL,9,Fmine and many others, there was
OL,10,Fnothing abstract about it," he said.
OL,12,F"Violence was not something you
OL,13,Fwatched on the news. It came into your
OL,14,Fhome, your conversations, your sense
OL,15,Fof safety and your future.
OL,17,F"Yvonne's death devastated. It created
OL,18,Fa wound that did not simply heal with
OL,19,Ftime. It changed the course of our
OL,20,Flives in ways we could never have
OL,21,Fimagined."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]tD@AOUyD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FHe added: "Violence does not end when
OL,7,Fthe act itself is over. It simply
OL,8,Fdoesn't.
OL,10,F"It travels through generations. It
OL,11,Fshapes relationships. It influences
OL,12,Fhow people see the world, how they
OL,13,Ftrust and how actually they cope.
OL,15,F"It creates anger, rage, bitterness
OL,16,Fand a deep sense of injustice that can
OL,17,Flast for decades. I know this because
OL,18,FI felt a lot of these emotions myself."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FHe said he found his faith in his 30s,
OL,7,Fnot coming from an overly religious
OL,8,Ffamily, but it became "central" to his
OL,9,Fprocessing of grief.
OL,11,F"I did forgive," he said.
OL,13,F"Forgiveness for me was not about
OL,14,Fexcusing what happened, what happened
OL,15,Fwas wrong and will forever be wrong.
OL,17,F"It was not about saying the act was
OL,18,Facceptable because it wasn't. It was
OL,19,Fnot about forgiving, nor was it about
OL,20,Fremoving responsibility from those who
OL,21,Fcarried it out.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@_O]sD@AOUsD@PO]uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
