PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"Forgiveness was something I did for
OL,7,Fmy own heart and my own peace."
OL,9,FTravis Dylan Frain, who survived the
OL,10,F2017 Westminster Bridge terrorist
OL,11,Fattack, also spoke at Stormont.
OL,13,FHe has since became an advocate for
OL,14,Fvictims of terrorism and fighting
OL,15,Fagainst violent extremism.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
