PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FWhile at university Mr Frain travelled
OL,7,Fto London on a study trip. He and his
OL,8,Ffriends were hit by a vehicle driven
OL,9,Fby an Islamist terrorist, Khalid
OL,10,FMasood. The attacker killed five
OL,11,Fpeople and injured more than fifty.
OL,13,FMr Frain was one of six British
OL,14,Fsurvivors of terrorism who co-founded
OL,15,Fthe charity Survivors Against Terror,
OL,16,Fto campaign for improvements in state
OL,17,Fsupport provided to victims of
OL,18,Fterrorism.
OL,20,FDescribing the attack, he said: "We
OL,21,Fdidn't have time to react.
OL,26,@|D@aOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"I remember I went atop the bonnet, I
OL,7,Fhit the windshield, and I remember
OL,8,Fbeing thrown into the earth for what
OL,9,Ffelt like forever, and of course it
OL,10,Fcould have only been a split second in
OL,11,Freality, if that.
OL,13,F"But it felt like forever that I was
OL,14,Fin the air. I had time to process what
OL,15,Fhad happened. I had time to realise
OL,16,Fthat I've been sort of flipped over in
OL,17,Fthe air."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FHe added: "The doctors were pretty
OL,7,Fclear afterwards that the only reason
OL,8,Fthat I survived was because when I
OL,9,Flanded, that down on the ground I
OL,10,Flanded on the left side of my body,
OL,11,Fand took a range of injuries, my head
OL,12,Factually landed on the stomach of one
OL,13,Fof the other lads in my group, who'd
OL,14,Fbeen knocked to the ground already."
OL,16,FHe said that like many others in the
OL,17,FUK, before the incident he was
OL,18,F"completely ignorant to these issues
OL,19,Fto terrorism and indeed to the
OL,20,FTroubles as well".
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@dO]zD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"I had to learn the hard way that
OL,7,Fthere was simply not enough support
OL,8,Ffor victims," he said
OL,10,F"And the way in which we support
OL,11,Fvictims of terrorism or not, is far
OL,12,Fmore indicative on us and our society
OL,13,Fthan it is on terrorists themselves.
OL,15,F"And I think it's incredibly important
OL,16,Fto remember that the whole point of
OL,17,Fterrorism is to reduce people's faith
OL,18,Fin the system and the systems that
OL,19,Fgovern us, and when we then fail to
OL,20,Fsupport those victims, we are doing
OL,21,Fthe terrorists' job for them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]rD@AOUwD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
