PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FHe added: "I know I'm a bit of an
OL,7,Foutsider as someone not affected by
OL,8,Fthe Troubles, but it means a lot to
OL,9,Fhave that connectedness and that peer-
OL,10,Fto-peer nature and to be here with you
OL,11,Fall, and I wish you all the best in
OL,12,Fyour efforts and accountability and
OL,13,Fjustice."
OL,15,FJohn Sproule's brother, Ian Sproule,
OL,16,Fwas killed by the provisional IRA at
OL,17,F24 years old, and the family believe
OL,18,Fthere was Garda collusion.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FHe said his mother never recovered
OL,7,Ffrom the loss of one of her sons and
OL,8,Fdied at 67 from a "broken heart".
OL,10,FMr Sproule said the Irish state "needs
OL,11,Fto step up and own its contribution to
OL,12,Fwhat happened".
OL,14,F"I will never stop seeking truth and
OL,15,Fjustice for Ian. There needs to be an
OL,16,Findependent public inquiry by the
OL,17,FIrish state. Ian was just not my
OL,18,Fbrother. He was also my best friend,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@`O]rD@aOUtD@NO]vD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,FThe event also heard from Denise
OL,7,FMullen, who was just four when her
OL,8,Ffather, Denis Mullen, was murdered by
OL,9,Fthe UVF in Moy, Co Tyrone, as part of
OL,10,Fthe Glenanne gang series of killings.
OL,12,FMr Gaston said the event was about
OL,13,F"about drawing a line of distinction
OL,14,Fbetween a victim-maker and a victim".
OL,16,F"When Europe pauses to reflect, there
OL,17,Fis a clear definition of what a victim
OL,18,Fis," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@dO]xD@AOUzD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"Directive 2017/541, on combat and
OL,7,Fterrorism, tells us that a victim is a
OL,8,Fnatural person who has suffered harm
OL,9,Fas a direct result of a terrorist
OL,10,Foffence.
OL,12,F"Sadly that is not the definition we
OL,13,Fhave here in Northern Ireland.
OL,15,F"In Northern Ireland, the definition
OL,16,Freads someone who is or has been
OL,17,Fphysically or psychologically injured
OL,18,Fas a result or a consequence of a
OL,19,Fconflict related incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1773144737
OL,3,C'A wound that does not heal', Families
OL,4,Cmark Day for Victims of Terrorism
OL,6,F"That is obnoxious, that is wrong, and
OL,7,Fwe must do all we can to ensure
OL,8,Fhistory isn't rewritten and that the
OL,9,Fterrorist injured by his own bomb by
OL,10,Fhis own hand, is not classed as a
OL,11,Fvictim."
OL,13,FUUP leader Jon Burrows said: "The pain
OL,14,Fand grief and trauma and loss of the
OL,15,FTroubles was permanent and profound
OL,16,Fand we've heard today how it ripples
OL,17,Fon through things like addictions,
OL,18,Fmental health and all kinds of other
OL,19,Fimpacts."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]uD@^OU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
